00:08:57.169 --> 00:09:03.169
Well, does it mean we have to all leave our Bethel homes now and go to the most distant parts of the earth?

00:09:03.169 --> 00:09:08.169
Well, remember, in Acts 1, 8, Jesus was speaking to people there in Jerusalem,

00:09:08.169 --> 00:09:16.169
and you may already be living in one of the most distant parts of the earth when you view it from Jerusalem's viewpoint.

00:09:16.169 --> 00:09:22.169
But the main thing is, wherever we are, if we can reach out and go somewhere else,

00:09:22.169 --> 00:09:28.169
or whether we can preach within our own territory, if we follow the example of these faithful ones,

00:09:28.169 --> 00:09:34.169
we'll be sure to try and reach out to persons who have not had the opportunity to hear the truth,

00:09:34.169 --> 00:09:36.169
